  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the Study is to investigate the prevalence of Helicobacter Pylori infection
      among the HIV/AIDS group. The study will screen the patients who were confirmed HIV/AIDS in
      Kaohsiung Medical University Hospital and collect the cases who were suspicious of
      Helicobacter Pylori infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
